":186264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T19:50:21.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"005773c263192cd840a45c30da9e0736cac45b26","tid":2396652,"uid":326733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T20:59:52.000Z","msg":"之前上網有睇過德國有啲大學program係用 英文授課， 如果我係零德文底我可唔可以報到 呢啲大學?<br />\n定係都係要先到當地上德文課達到一個水平先可以報？<br />\nThanks"},{"pid":"057bcd1d81234e43eed80e279210314676b7876e","tid":2396652,"uid":85612,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"005773c263192cd840a45c30da9e0736cac45b26","tid":2396652,"uid":326733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T20:59:52.000Z","msg":"之前上網有睇過德國有啲大學program係用 英文授課， 如果我係零德文底我可唔可以報到 呢啲大學?<br />\n定係都係要先到當地上德文課達到一個水平先可以報？<br />\nThanks"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T22:18:41.000Z","msg":"如果個課程講到明係全英文嘅話，應該係真係可以剩係用英文上堂、交paper、考試同畢業。不過有啲course係有寫hybrid language(一半德文一半英文)，依類型就多數預你畢業前德文要去一定水平，甚至可能有啲core/elective會用德文教。<br />\n<br />\n係德國日常生活完全唔識德文會幾唔方便，始終德國唔係北歐，唔係個個人識聽識講英文。學有餘力都會建議學下。"},{"pid":"3f67bfd2aaeaad7dee51d1c9ac45bed747845573","tid":2396652,"uid":380159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f73ba80b23527577245c5302938c1d8f54636006","tid":2396652,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"372faef0be3eb1e38c161d6b73f972fe3aef533a","tid":2396652,"uid":380159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T19:40:21.000Z","msg":"KIT留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T18:19:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> KIT 讀咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T09:11:57.000Z","msg":"讀緊PHD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前都係major physics"},{"pid":"f7a3acb12c73a807a57f14e7de32427c917f2420","tid":2396652,"uid":200475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T10:40:12.000Z","msg":"想問下TUM Informat